Project 1 "Average.py"

This project will be a code written in Python. The code will allow a user
to enter grades then average them out.

To display this code you will need to download Notepad++
To run this code you will need to open command prompt on your computer.

The code will be making a user, input as many grades as they want. 
The code will first ask you "Hello, how many grades will you be entering today?". 
Then after you decide how many grades you will be entering
it will then say "Please enter grade [Number]". Finally the code will average the set of
grades given by the user, then display The average.




